### Welcome
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### Get All Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events

###

### Get Single Event
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/1

###

### Get Event - Not Found (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/999

###

### Create New Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "AI Workshop",
  "date": "2026-08-01",
  "venue": "Seminar Hall B",
  "maxSeats": 30
}

###

### Register for Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events/register/new
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "email": "ravi@college.com",
  "rollNumber": "CS2024001",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Register Again - Duplicate Check (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events/register/new
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "email": "ravi@college.com",
  "rollNumber": "CS2024001",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Bad Data - Validation Test (400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events/register/new
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentName": "",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

###

### Get All Registrations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/registrations/all

###

### Get by Roll Number
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/registrations/CS2024001

###

### Unknown Route - 404
GET http://localhost:3000/api/unknown
